The course deals in deptht more complicated legal problems of companies, incl. shareholder remedies, notarial practice, drafting of companies legal documentation and arrangement of legal relations in companies.Objectives/eesmärkid:  The aim of the course is to provide students practical knowledge about relations between different regulations of the company law and a knowledge how to use this knowledge in solving of practical cases and drawing legal documents.Learning outcomes/õpiväljund:  Student completing this course should: 1) be able to find out company law problems, to find a legal qualification and to provide systematic and logic solution of the case; 2) know company law on exhaustive level; 3) understand company law remedies and is able to implement them.
